<div class="container py-5 text-center">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <h1 class="display-1 fw-bold text-danger">500</h1>
            <h2 class="text-secondary mb-4">Internal Server Error</h2>
            <p class="lead">
              We sorry all of you. something wnet wrong on my server. my engineer solving this promblem
